Yeah,

00:44:28.980 --> 00:44:29.520
kind of just

00:44:29.520 --> 00:44:30.480
two-way data binding

00:44:30.480 --> 00:44:31.940
on the values there.

00:44:31.940 --> 00:44:33.020
Exactly,

