00:45:14.340 --> 00:45:16.460
and we kind of made

00:45:16.460 --> 00:45:17.100
design Reflex

00:45:17.100 --> 00:45:18.300
to be really performant

00:45:18.300 --> 00:45:20.100
in everything we do.

00:45:20.100 --> 00:45:21.520
And the reason we use

00:45:21.520 --> 00:45:22.140
WebSockets

00:45:22.140 --> 00:45:23.400
is because Reflex apps,

00:45:23.400 --> 00:45:23.740
especially,

00:45:23.740 --> 00:45:23.940
like,

00:45:23.940 --> 00:45:24.860
