00:46:14.500 --> 00:46:15.920
over the WebSocket.

00:46:15.920 --> 00:46:17.600
So all of this

00:46:17.600 --> 00:46:17.980
was done

00:46:17.980 --> 00:46:19.120
in the name of performance

